{"id": "1251192187513733131", "channel_id": "1251179111414632509", "type": 0, "author_id": "771169877121564703", "author_name": "yang_42", "author_bot": false, "content": "米粒觉醒完3次不用弃牌的话最快的情况下:\n第一回合\n觉醒一次,下回合开始给6费觉醒\n第二回合\n拿到了6费觉醒,6费太贵打不出,等下回合预备减3费才打\n第三回合\n打出第2个觉醒,下回合开始给9费觉醒,9费太贵打不出,等两回合后预备减了6费才打\n第四回合\n拿到了9费卡\n第五回合\n9变6费\n第六回合\n6费3费,终于能打出了", "timestamp": "2024-06-14T15:11:03.530000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251179111414632509", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "有关米粒的讨论（开个楼专门讨论下）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179716706619494"]}
{"id": "1251192401226367089", "channel_id": "1251179111414632509", "type": 0, "author_id": "771169877121564703", "author_name": "yang_42", "author_bot": false, "content": "当然你也可以用鼠鼠钥令补一下费提前任意觉醒1回合", "timestamp": "2024-06-14T15:11:54.483000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251179111414632509", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "有关米粒的讨论（开个楼专门讨论下）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179716706619494"]}
{"id": "1251192662627848233", "channel_id": "1251179111414632509", "type": 0, "author_id": "771169877121564703", "author_name": "yang_42", "author_bot": false, "content": "最优方法还是用弃牌的方式来让原拉拉出来0费直接开", "timestamp": "2024-06-14T15:12:56.806000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251179111414632509", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "有关米粒的讨论（开个楼专门讨论下）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179716706619494"]}
{"id": "1251193151520112800", "channel_id": "1251179111414632509", "type": 0, "author_id": "771169877121564703", "author_name": "yang_42", "author_bot": false, "content": "如果坚持6费就打出的话风险过高,你一整回合亏了其他人的狂和技能,暖个屁直接死了", "timestamp": "2024-06-14T15:14:53.367000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251179111414632509", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "有关米粒的讨论（开个楼专门讨论下）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179716706619494"]}
{"id": "1251194148934127728", "channel_id": "1251179111414632509", "type": 0, "author_id": "771169877121564703", "author_name": "yang_42", "author_bot": false, "content": "最终觉醒还有个隐藏坏处就是他给的神国卡其实是\"置入抽牌堆\"的,你仍需要浪费1个抽牌机会来抽他出来,配合\"执妄\"会更进一步减少你抽到能用的牌,所以米粒是极其依赖法洛思或抽牌造物的", "timestamp": "2024-06-14T15:18:51.169000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-14T15:20:09.778000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251179111414632509", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "有关米粒的讨论（开个楼专门讨论下）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179716706619494"]}
